Class Dataset

  • Direct Known Subclasses:

    public abstract class Dataset
extends java.lang.Object
    Class which represents a dataset. Each dataset contains training-instances, test-instances and cv-instances (usually cv-instances are all available instances). Furthermore a dataset contains also the information about the learning task (CollectorPreferences) (e.g. a multilabel-dataset contains a MultilabelCollector in the CollectorPreferences).

    MK
